-MP

creation du graphe de dependance 

-include 
https://www.gnu.org/software/make/manual/html_node/Include.html


$<  = premiere dependance. 

$^ = toutes les dependances 

$@	= nom de la regle 
	${NAME} : ${OBJS}
	${CXX} ${OBJS} -o ${NAME}
	ici ce sera ${NAME}

-I	= cherchera le dossier include
	https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/cpp/preprocessor/hash-include-directive-c-cpp?view=msvc-170

@D = variable automatique/implicite correspondant au dossier de la target
	ici ${OBJS}%.o

https://www.gnu.org/software/make/manual/html_node/Automatic-Variables.html

